<!-- -*-markdown-*- -->
# Changelog 
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog][1]
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning][2].

## [Unreleased]

## [1.0.0] - 2018-01-14
### Added
- mpdburn.sh - burn currently loaded mpd playlist.
- ripalbum.sh - rip music album to mp3 V0.
- ec, ep - call emacsclient easily and automatically.
- cmake - to make it easier to use on new systems.
- Changelog, AUTHORS

### Changed
- Symlinks: NEWS->Changelog, README->README.md, COPYING->LICENSE.
- Moved scripts to language-based subdirectories.
### Removed
- Cruftfiles (~, #)

[1]: http://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/
[2]: http://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html
